item.title: ● Identifications For Top Of Screen ●
item.dc:creator: @paolucci paolucci
item.description:
@paolucci wrote:

You mean pressing ctrl+F and finding the text to change the writing on top of screen? if its the finding your after i can help.

Difficulty: 1/10
I’m using ‘Freescape’

search this:

"//Playercount and server name at top of screen" (without quotation marks of course!)

Then a few lines underneath their should be something saying like @red@ or a different word of a colour inside. So you would write your name in colours like this:

@red@~@whi@H@red@O@gre@L@cya@Y@whi@p@red@k~

That’s just an example from my server.

Tell me if you need a bit more info so i can edit.

Read full topic
